<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-63-0161 </DOCNO><TEXT>A research and development project is under way to specify, design, construct,and evaluate a user interface system to meet the unique requirementsof a delivery vehicle for a knowledge-based system applied to gas turbineelectronics equipment maintenance and troubleshooting. The user interfaceis a portable device with text display, video and overlay graphics display,voice recognition and speech production, special-function keypad, andprinter. A modular software structure based on a serial communicationsprotocol between user interface device and expert system host computerprovides flexibility, expandability, and a simple, effective user interfacedialogue.</TEXT></DOC>